[Enable Debug Menu]
author=Hacc
description=Enter options at the title screen and press circle to access it. The "x" setting means that the option is disabled, and the "0" setting means that it is enabled. Your setting for each of the options will become active when you exit both the SYSTEM MENU and DEBUG MENU. Then, start a new or continued game. But, due to the DEBUG MENU not always showing up, when you try to activate it in the option menu, go to the AREA SELECT MENU within the DEBUG MENU instead, and choose the stage you want to go to. If you want the complete guide on how to use it, pm me.
patch=1,EE,EE2086FA,extended,50894046
patch=1,EE,EE208602,extended,50894606

